name: Destra Network
description: Destra Network: Building the Web3 AI Stack Destra is a decentralized AI-native network, purpose-built to run autonomous agents, decentralized compute, and real-world infrastructure. From inference to execution, Destra unifies the essential layers of Web3—AI, compute, privacy, and economics—into one composable ecosystem. At the core lies $DSYNC, a deflationary utility token that powers and captures value from every product interaction across the network.
